Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.53,0:00:02.37,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}那麼… 還不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.18,0:00:04.38,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}我親手…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:05.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:08.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴！ 佳乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:04.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這傷痕恐怕要留下一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對不起  國崎  神尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:11.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們倒是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.61,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是佳乃小時候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.60,AIR Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,770)}羽   毛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:31.09,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們的母親去世後的第一個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.32,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看啊看啊  姐姐  是氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:44.79,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那邊那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.46,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}買了那個的話  是不是就能飛上天空了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.21,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要是一個氣球就能把人帶上天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個攤子不早就飛上天了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.59,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦… 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:56.63,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}姐姐真聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:03:00.56,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但那就是說  只要有很多氣球就可以飛起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.53,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯… 大概能吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.50,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過  只能買一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:14.53,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算只有一個  只要把它吹得很大就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:18.19,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那樣的話  就算再重的東西也可以帶起來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:20.94,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那樣一來可就買不了別的東西了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:22.13,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.28,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.44,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  謝謝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.46,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃一直想飛到天上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.42,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為她相信那樣就可以見到母親了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:44.89,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我告訴過她  媽媽在天上注視著佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.78,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}父親和我都不忍告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:52.18,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:02.44,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}接下來  發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼也沒有發生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:54.46,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是誰在這裏胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.61,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}於是我們把羽毛放回原處  回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:12.58,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經去不了媽媽那裏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.84,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從第二天開始  佳乃就變得有些異常了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:18.07,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有時會害怕強光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:21.07,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有時會不知不覺地走到外邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:24.48,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且有時還會嘟囔一些莫名其妙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:29.31,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有一天夜晚  我醒來時發現佳乃不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.79,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我慌忙去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.27,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}才發現她在這間診療室裏用手術刀割傷了自己的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:38.14,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好在處理及時  才沒有大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:42.34,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那時候我就想  這不是佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.16,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而是其他什麼人在扮演著佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是所謂的多重人格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:51.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也許吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.67,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是一條神奇的緞帶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:56.87,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要一直把它戴到長大為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.49,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你就可以使用魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.33,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  無論碰到什麼事都不要把它解開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:08.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是這樣啊  送給佳乃緞帶的原來是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在她失去理智想要割傷手腕的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到這條緞帶就會找回自我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我小時候這樣想來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃也並不記得多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:22.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從一開始就不存在什麼魔法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:26.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我那時候下定決心要繼承父親的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:31.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為我認為  成為醫生就可以治好佳乃的病了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃碰過的那根羽毛到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:35.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:39.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像是從很久以前就被供奉在那所神社裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但管理人也並不知道更多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}會不會是那根羽毛的詛咒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:49.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}作為醫生是不能認同這種理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過那有可能是誘發心病的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:58.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個時候的佳乃剛剛失去母親  心理壓力很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想這才應該是根本的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天也要去霧島那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  而且還有零工要做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我過一會兒也想去看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:11.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}交到新朋友不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨晚  我又做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:20.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是一個在天空中飛翔的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:24.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自從那之後  我就在夢中漸漸地追溯著時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:31.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在昨晚的夢中  我在天空中很悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:32.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}悲傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:38.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我像從前一樣在天上飛翔著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:42.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且我在那裏感到很悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:47.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在那麼清爽的微風中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:52.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼我還會那樣悲傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那不是夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}與你無關的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:57.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你要是不笑的話就會連我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:01.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:03.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  你還是笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:06.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}V
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:18.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！ 國崎往人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:31.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你怎麼會來這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我還想問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你撿那種玩意  難不成在搞廢品回收嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:39.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的興趣就是在這種地方撿東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是世上最無聊的興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:43.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你少管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:50.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真羨慕你啊  每天只是玩就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}國崎往人還不是和我差不多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:56.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可是要幹活的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天也正要去工作的地方幹活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？ 上廁所嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是  看那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那莫非就是遠野的母親？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:21.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:25.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:37.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美風  看上去很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吶  向美風打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想她一個人一定會很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  我去打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}遠野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:58.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}國崎先生在這裏做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  和小滿一起散步來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:03.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦…  哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那傢伙去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:08.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和小滿在一起的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  剛才的確是在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:16.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}關於剛才和我在一起的那個人  小滿說過什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:19.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼也沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎  那就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個人是你的母親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:25.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:29.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我從前幫她搬過東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說起來  你們倆給人的感覺的確很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我對那個人來說  是夢的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:38.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別逃啊  土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來  讓你涼快涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}挺有精神的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:59.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  往人  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對不起  昨晚又給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒什麼大不了的  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦  你來了  國崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天也有很多工作要做喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.77,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃還在睡午覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:27.43,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  考慮到昨晚的事  我讓她休息去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.39,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也該起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.18,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:32.71,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:35.11,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:45.27,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想往人會相信我的  所以才寫了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:48.23,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我還是決定到天上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.34,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那樣的話  我想大家就都會幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:56.26,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感覺也會碰到往人正在尋找的那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.67,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然不知道是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.94,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我一定會把她帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:04.83,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在那之前  希望你能照看我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:08.27,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其實  姐姐很勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:12.77,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}另外  脖子的傷真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:34.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:41.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}振作點  佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有外傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:46.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那這血是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:50.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有出血的跡象  看來沒有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:52.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她要從這裏到天上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:06.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了  往人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:15.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知為什麼  心境很亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像很熟悉  又好像很悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓佳乃躺下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:33.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}國崎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:47.26,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的名字叫白穗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.40,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}無論如何請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:56.29,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我記得那時的秋天是很美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.41,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他是我們夫婦的第一個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:04.58,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在他的右手腕有一塊天生的痣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}村民們都說這不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.80,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我們卻並沒有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.85,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}八雲哭鬧起來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.52,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我便會將母親教給我的搖籃曲唱給他聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:21.66,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聽到這個八雲便會平靜下來  但只有這一天不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:38.39,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我本想  這根羽毛一定是神賜給我們的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:53.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}帶走！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.65,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}戰爭開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.14,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的丈夫再也沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:11.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個村子裏有沒有人撿到了發光的羽毛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}羽毛是邪惡的東西  碰過那個的人都給我站出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:19.15,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我趁著那個夜晚逃了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:37.45,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就這樣  我來到了這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:46.26,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神社的宮司熱心收留了我們母子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:50.48,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我本以為在這個安寧的小村子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:54.47,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可以和八雲一起開始新的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:58.67,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  在那一年的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.83,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}村子裏流行起了瘟疫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.07,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很多人死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.85,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}宮司先生  這孩子怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已經渡過危險期了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天亮後燒也就會退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:17.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  村民們認為是你們母子帶來的瘟疫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:18.60,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不該讓你們住到這裏來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這裏祭奠著「巫女神」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:30.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「巫女神」會給為這片土地帶來災難的人刻上烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:33.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果知道這孩子有痣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:36.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他們一定會逼著你將孩子獻給神的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:41.06,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}難道要將這孩子作為活祭品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這片土地就是這樣平靜災禍的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.84,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這孩子是我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:53.33,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是丈夫留給我的唯一的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:54.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你還是放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:57.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不然連你也會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.97,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那麼  還不如我親手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.04,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.92,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.19,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}世上怎麼會有殺死自己孩子的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.37,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算是自己的孩子會使世界毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.99,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也不會有殺死自己孩子的母親的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.83,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓我來… 代替他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.62,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.33,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}救救這個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別做傻事！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.20,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.02,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽你在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:03.69,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:09.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有什麼想吃的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已經吃過很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:16.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有想要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:23.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為姐姐在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還有土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:32.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和我的新朋友們
